            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-941] Standardize on a common mocking framework (either EasyMock or Mockito)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-941</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>We are currently using EasyMock in the caching module and Mockito in the main module. While Mockito appears to have a somewhat nicer API, the sheer number of test cases based on EasyMock in the caching module makes it much simpler to replace Mockito with EasyMock than the other way around.</description>
